{"tid":424770,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【尋人】舊情人","createTime":"2017-10-05T05:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T00:15:09.000Z","uid":124343,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5adbc1d4f4fbe3ed2059e02bcfb99fef038a9838","tid":424770,"uid":124343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:29:51.000Z","msg":"借人ac開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同佢係2012年一齊<br />\n<br />\n見到隔離post巴打尋人<br />\n我都覺得可以係呢到試下搵<br />\n小小背景資料：<br />\n佢個名係：chu sheung wai barry/ andy chu<br />\n92年出世<br />\n中學係讀St. Joseph's College<br />\n2012年同佢拍拖嘅時候佢讀緊hku mbbs<br />\n跟住拍拍下<br />\n佢話要去返英國（佢出生地）讀書<br />\n仲連fb個D都del哂<br />\n去到2014個陣都仲間唔中有聯絡<br />\n佢每次轉電話都會wtsapp返我<br />\n問我讀書讀成點 etc.<br />\n但無啦啦去到前年就無左佢消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以好想搵返佢,知道佢近況如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我無記錯佢中學係有幾個好兄弟<br />\n如果你地知道嘅<br />\n麻煩telegram我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/johnjohn123123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjohnjohn123123&d=qm%2FEjCb%2BruC%2FKbOXS6utqACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d446c03a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/johnjohn123123</a><br />\n<br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fb37fb075fd53df06ef401be5dfc9d06cc9d50","tid":424770,"uid":128101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:33:46.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36eb4dbbda3cafbf900c929f7f7eab111e1f0b8","tid":424770,"uid":124343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf94d2c3a51be086a7cf54af36e14a91947f2276","tid":424770,"uid":140696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b597821